       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ACTRECON2.
      * CARD-ACTIVATION EXCEPTION QUEUE FOR THE THIRTY-DAY WINDOW.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DAYS-SINCE-ISSUE PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-ACTIVATED        PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01  WS-ACTION           PIC X(8) VALUE 'REVIEW'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-DAYS-SINCE-ISSUE
           ACCEPT WS-ACTIVATED
           PERFORM 2000-ROUTE-ACCOUNT
           DISPLAY 'ACTION: ' WS-ACTION
           STOP RUN.
       2000-ROUTE-ACCOUNT.
           MOVE 'REVIEW' TO WS-ACTION
           IF WS-DAYS-SINCE-ISSUE > 30
              IF WS-ACTIVATED = 'N'
                 MOVE 'SEEKOTP' TO WS-ACTION
              ELSE
                 MOVE 'ACTIVE' TO WS-ACTION
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE 'WAIT' TO WS-ACTION
           END-IF.
